cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.DS 

The paper presents algorithms for learning regularizers that improve generalization in machine learning. This topic is closely related to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), and data structures (cs.DS). Given that the paper focuses on developing algorithms for improving generalization in machine learning, cs.LG is the most likely sub-category. However, the paper's focus on regularizers and their relationship to generalization could also make it relevant to the other sub-categories listed.
